description: Gyro Twins authentic Greek cuisine is taking Charlotte by storm! Made from the freshest quality ingredients around, this is food you can really sink your teeth into. Gyro, Halloumi, Bifteki, and more fantastic food on pita bread is making it's way to you today! So if you're looking for a unique eating experience on the streets of Charlotte, be on the lookout for Gyro Twins!
name: Gyro Twins Truck
